    Intent tests for the camera fragment.

    Simple class that handles the opening of the camera for QR scanning by extending zxing library's CaptureActivity class.

    This Class represents a Comment that will belong to a QRCode object.

    This class is a custom adapter to handle Comment objects

    Main app activity.

    MapFragment

    Interface to handle long clicking on the RecyclerView
    PhotoUploader
    A simple object that contains the name and image url of an uploaded photo, that is added to the "uploads" collection in the Firebase database.

    Handles player profile screen.

    TakePhotoActivity
    The activity responsible for taking a photo of the QR object or location, and then uploading it to Firebase.
    TakePhotoActivity.OnUploadListener

    ToolbarTest
    Toolbar button tests Tests every button on the toolbar and their interactions with the main screen
    ViewQR
    This is the dialog fragment that appears when a user clicks to see more info about a certain QRCode.
    ViewQR.ViewQRDialogListener
